<table border=0 cellpadding=7 cellspacing=0 width=100%>
	<tr>
		<td class=bod>
			<center>	
			Welcome to my website!  It was last updated 08 July 2000.
			</center>

			<p align=justify> 
			Here, I shall chronicle my attempts at brushing up on my programming
			skills, and learning the 
			<a href="http://www.talula.demon.co.uk/allegro/">Allegro Game
			Programming Library</a>.  I'll keep my last 5 projects on the front
			page for easy viewing.  Yes, I realize that it isn't actually
			<b>shaniber.net</b>, but someday, baby, someday!
			</p>

			<p align=justify>
			My current setup at home is a cobbled together AMD K6-233 with
			64MB of RAM and a 4GB of hard drive.  I'm running Windows 98.  
			I'm using <a href="http://msdn.microsoft.com/vstudio/">
			Microsoft Visual Studio 6 Pro</a>, <a href="http://www.delorie.com">
			the latest DJPGG from Delorie Software</a>, and the 
			<a href="http://sunsite.auc.dk/allegro/wip.html">3.9.32 WIP
			of Allegro</a>.  Right now, I'm just posting the source code for my
			projects, but I'm hoping to work them up into a sort of tutorial for
			people who are just starting out.
			</p>

		</td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td class=bod>
